s the Telegram `/status` built-in command and not an HTTP/CLI JSON endpoint. If an operator-facing JSON `/status` endpoint exists elsewhere, that path was not updated. Severity: minor\n++\n++## Verdict: PASS WITH NOTES\n++\n++## Notes for Lead Agent\n++1. Consider updating `CypherClawArt.status_display()` to emit an explicit unavailable fallback string when `ollama` is provided but `instances` is empty.\n++2. Clarify and align the required surface for this subtask: Telegram `/status` command vs daemon status endpoint JSON, then decide whether additional endpoint-level wiring is needed.\n+diff --git a/sdp/verification/t-012@20260416t043834z-manual-verify.md b/sdp/verification/t-012@20260416t043834z-manual-verify.md\n+new file mode 100644\n+index 0000000..ecd5d96\n+--- /dev/null\n++++ b/sdp/verification/t-012@20260416t043834z-manual-verify.md\n+@@ -0,0 +1,50 @@\n++# Manual Verification Report — T-012@20260416T043834Z\n++\n++**Method:** manual\n++**Actor:** codex\n++**Date:** 2026-04-16T05:24:40.733846Z\n++**New Run:** run-manual-t-012@20260416t043834z-1776317080\n++**Supersedes Run:** run-t-012@20260416t043834z-1776315429\n++**Git Commit SHA:** 7df9deab039d9a0b7a01734b130e821247010c25\n++**Dirty Worktree:** True\n++\n++## What Was Checked\n++\n++ScoreTree JSON round-trip preserves nested commission, brief, form, motif, section, harmonic, arrangement, and narrative fields; PieceQueue writes active score-tree JSON to configurable active_path, recovers active trees from either queue ledger or active file, and preserves queued tree restart behavior; duet composer calls set_active(score_tree) when a gated score-tree piece starts.\n++\n++## Tests / Commands Run\n++\n++- `PROMPTCLAW_PETS_FILE=/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/.sdp/tmp/pets.json pytest tests/test_score_tree.py tests/test_score_tree_composer.py tests/test_piece_queue.py tests/test_repertoire_memory_score_tree.py -q`\n++- `ruff check my-claw/tools/senseweave/score_tree.py my-claw/tools/senseweave/piece_queu